\nis sadhana for XYZ years. Why is God not coming?&quot; Wait patiently. After all=\r\n, if you have truly surrendered, why is it a problem then to wait, let us s=\r\nay, 1000 years for Her grace? If you say &quot;I want Her to come in 1 year or 1=\r\n0 years and not 1000 years&quot;, that means you have not fully surrendered.\n&gt; \n=\r\n&gt; * * *\n&gt; \n&gt; &gt; How to measure it?\n&gt; \n&gt; One can measure it by seeing how one=\r\n is internally reacting to challenging circumstances that would earlier pro=\r\nvoke lust, anger, greed, jealosy etc inside one.\n&gt; \n&gt; However, what will on=\r\ne do by measuring? It is not like one can turn a knob based on the measurem=\r\nent to correct it.\n&gt; \n&gt; In fact, when surrender is completeone you will sto=\r\np measuring or even thinking about how to measure it.\n&gt; \n&gt; Best regards,\n&gt; =\r\nNarasimha\n&gt; ------------ --------- --------- --------- --------- --------- =\r\n-\n&gt; Free Jyotish Software, Free Jyotish Lessons, Jyotish Writings,\n&gt; &quot;Do It=\r\n Yourself&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpana:\n&gt; http://www.V=\r\nedicAst rologer.org\n&gt; Films that make a difference: http://SaraswatiFil ms.=\r\norg\n&gt; Spirituality: http://groups. yahoo.com/ group/vedic- wisdom\n&gt; Jyotish=\r\n writings: http://groups. yahoo.com/ group/JyotishWri tings\n&gt; ------------ =\r\n--------- --------- --------- --------- --------- -\n&gt; \n&gt; ---- vedic_pathak =\r\n&lt;vedic_pathak@ yahoo.com&gt; wrote: \n&gt; &gt; Namaste,\n&gt; &gt; \n&gt; &gt; &gt; Easiest thing to =\r\ndo is Ishwar(Ishwari) pranidhana. Surrender to &gt;God. I freely admitted to t=\r\nhe Lord when I had His darshana that I &gt;was a complete fool \n&gt; &gt; \n&gt; &gt; I sin=\r\ncerely wish to surrender to Mother completely. I am trying hard. I wish to =\r\nsurrender my ego, anger, passions as well as all good qualities... .\n&gt; &gt; \n&gt;=\r\n &gt; How to achieve it effectivey? How to measure it?\n&